data.description:
Welcome to 924 Filly Ln in the heart of Temple, TX! This charming 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is located in an established and sought-after neighborhood.

As you step inside, you'll be impressed with the new paint, flooring, and baseboards that give this home a fresh and modern feel. The large windows throughout the home allow plenty of natural light to pour in, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.

The large master bedroom is a true sanctuary, complete with an ensuite bathroom and ample closet space. The two additional bedrooms are generously sized and share a full bathroom.

The bonus room is an ideal space for a home office or second living area, providing versatility to suit your lifestyle. The cozy fireplace in the living room is perfect for chilly evenings and adds a touch of character to the home.

The 2-car garage provides ample storage and parking space, and the backyard is the perfect place to unwind and relax. This home is a must see!
